ion-template</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fregante/browser-extension-template\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">609</span></span></a> - Barebones boilerplate with parcel, options handler and auto-publishing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rpl/create-webextension\">create-webextension</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rpl/create-webextension\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">20</span></span></a> - Yarn WebExtension generator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://extensionizr.com\">extensionizr.com</a> - Web UI that helps you create an initial configuration and files.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webextension-toolbox/generator-web-extension\">generator-web-extension</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/webextension-toolbox/generator-web-extension\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-t